{
  "description": "Endpoint -> host derivation vectors (the Zone facade). control_host = api.<zone>; data_host = <sandbox_id>.computer.<zone> (port-suffixed on non-secure local zones); secure unless localhost/*.localhost/lvh.me/*.lvh.me.",
  "valid": [
